"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.13.9\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.13.9</span> 標題：廢丘、土丘、土堆（tell, mound）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גַּל, נצה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gal (nitsim))</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:25\">2KI 19:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:28\">JOB 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:2\">ISA 25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:26\">ISA 37:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:10\">JER 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:37\">JER 51:37</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מְעִי, מַפָּלָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： m‘i mapalah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:1\">ISA 17:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עִי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘i)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:1\">PSA 79:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:18\">JER 26:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:6\">MIC 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:12\">MIC 3:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： תֵּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17\">DEU 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:28\">JOS 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:13\">JOS 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18\">JER 30:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:2\">JER 49:2</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0424_tell.jpg\" alt=\"廢丘（伯善）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">廢丘（伯善） (© Grauesel, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>廢丘是指某地建於多個不同時期的城鎮，由於多次被毀和重建而形成的一座小山。聖地有許多個廢丘，其中有很多已被挖掘出來，而且已被確認是聖經中提到的古代城鎮。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>古代的城鎮經常會被戰爭摧毀，或者在瘟疫、饑荒過後被遺棄；隨著時間的推移，城鎮中的建築也會倒塌。新城市往往直接建造在舊城市的廢墟上，並不完全清除舊城市的基礎和建設。這個在舊建築上面建造新建築的過程，逐漸形成了一座人工的山丘或土丘。在聖經的描述中，這些土丘代表著毀壞和衰敗。然而，建造在這些土丘上的城鎮地勢較高，因而更容易防禦。</p>\n<p>除了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:13\">JOS 11:13</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18\">JER 30:18</a> 可能是例外，上面列出的所有詞語都含有某種負面的意思，不是僅僅指上面建有城市的土丘，而是指毀滅性活動所導致的一堆廢墟。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:2\">JER 49:2</a> ：原文字面意為「它必成為一個荒廢的土丘」的分可以譯為：「它必成為一座由廢墟覆蓋的小山」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）。有些譯本沒有保留文中關於高度的元素，譯為「它必成為廢墟」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 提供了一個很值得借鑒的翻譯範例，譯為「拉巴必成為一堆瓦礫。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
